<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>ema525_02_SU_0003_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema525_su_01.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema525_01_su_0003">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="1" lang="y">상자를 둘러싸고 있는 도형을 살펴봅시다.
        </h2>
      </section>
        
      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y">상자를 둘러싸고 있는 사각형을 살펴보며 상자를 어떻게 분류할 수 있을지 이야기해 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="wrap flex justify-conter col gap_20" >          
            <div class="contents_img">
              <ul class="example_num">
                <li lang="y" class="f24b"><span>가</span></li>
                <li lang="y" class="f24b"><span>나</span></li>
                <li lang="y" class="f24b"><span>다</span></li>
                <li lang="y" class="f24b"><span>라</span></li>
                <li lang="y" class="f24b"><span>마</span></li>
                <li lang="y" class="f24b"><span>바</span></li>
              </ul>
              <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA525_01_SU/0003_contents1.png" alt="직육면체,정육면체 예시 이미지"/>
            </div>
            <div class="text-align-center">
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                <div class="example_box">
                  <p lang="y">1보다 큰 수를 곱하면 계산 결과는 곱해지는 수보다 커지므로 색점토를 더 많이 사용한 사람은 예린입니다.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div> 
        </article>
        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3 lang="y">직사각형으로 둘러싸인 상자를 모두 찾아 기호를 찾아 보세요.</h3>     
          <div class="contents_img">
            <div class="boolean_wrap">
              <button data-answer-single="true"><span class="f24b">가</span></button>
              <button data-answer-single="false"><span class="f24b">나</span></button>
              <button data-answer-single="true"><span class="f24b">다</span></button>
              <button data-answer-single="false"><span class="f24b">라</span></button>
              <button data-answer-single="true"><span class="f24b">마</span></button>
              <button data-answer-single="true"><span class="f24b">바</span></button>
            </div>
            <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA525_01_SU/0003_contents2.png" alt="직육면체,정육면체 예시 이미지"/>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_3">
          <h3 lang="y">정사각형으로 둘러싸인 상자를 모두 찾아 기호를 찾아 보세요.</h3>     
          <div class="contents_img">
            <div class="boolean_wrap">
              <button data-answer-single="false"><span class="f24b">가</span></button>
              <button data-answer-single="false"><span class="f24b">나</span></button>
              <button data-answer-single="true"><span class="f24b">다</span></button>
              <button data-answer-single="false"><span class="f24b">라</span></button>
              <button data-answer-single="true"><span class="f24b">마</span></button>
              <button data-answer-single="false"><span class="f24b">바</span></button>
            </div>
            <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA525_01_SU/0003_contents2.png" alt="직육면체,정육면체 예시 이미지"/>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_4">
          <div class="summarize_wrap yellow">
            <div class="summarize promise">
              <label lang="y">약속해 볼까요</label>

              <div>
                <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA525_01_SU/0003_contents3.png" alt="직육면체 예제 이미지"/>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span lang="y">직사각형 6개로 둘러싸인 도형을 </span>
                <button class="reveal_btn" data-pair="직육면체" lang="y">직육면체</button>
                <span lang="y" class="small-gap">라고 합니다.</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA525_01_SU/0003_contents4.png" alt="정육면체 예제 이미지"/>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span lang="y">정사각형 6개로 둘러싸인 도형을</span>
                <button class="reveal_btn" data-pair="정육면체" lang="y">정육면체</button>
                <span lang="y" class="small-gap">라고 합니다.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          <button class="btnSubmit">제출</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
